Conflicts: claws-mail (>= 2.0.1)
Recommends: claws-mail-plugins
Description: This plugin is intended to extend the filtering possibilities of Claws Mail. It provides a Perl interface to Claws Mail' filtering mechanism, allowing the use of full Perl power in email filters.
